6.30	Secretary's_Day_(The_Office)	Secretary's Day (The Office)	"Secretary's Day" is the 22nd episode of the sixth season of the U.S. comedy series The Office and the show's 122nd episode overall. It aired on April 22, 2010 on NBC. It was written by Mindy Kaling, who portrays Kelly Kapoor on the series, and directed by Steve Carell, who portrays Michael Scott. It is also the second episode he has directed for the series.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/fd/Andy_with_cake_smashed_in_his_face.jpg/250px-Andy_with_cake_smashed_in_his_face.jpg
